<section class="intro">
  <div class="intro-inner">
    <div class="container">
      <img class="intro-logo" src="/assets/images/logo-uofthacks-line--white.svg" alt="" />

      <p class="intro-tagline">The University of Toronto's <br><strong>3<sup>rd</sup></strong> annual hackathon is almost here.</p>

      <div class="row">
        <form class="" action="#" method="post">
          <div class="input-group">
            <input class="intro-input" type="email" name="email-intro" placeholder="Email address">
            <input class="intro-btn btn-uh-green btn" type="submit" name="name" value="Subscribe to updates">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<header class="site-header" role="navigation">
  <div class="site-header-inner">
    <div class="container">
      <ul class="site-header-links nav text-center">
        <% data.header.navigation.each do |link| %>
        <li class="site-header-link"><%= link_to link.name, link.url, :data => { :scroll => nil } %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section id="about" class="text section--md">
  <header class="section-header">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="section-header-title">About</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="section-body">
    <div class="container container--sm">
      <p class="lead text-center">
        We are the the University of Toronto's<br> annual hackathon.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>/ˈhakəθɒn/</strong>: An event, typically lasting several days, in which a large number of people meet to engage in collaborative computer programming.
      </p>

      <p>
        We look past this traditional definition of a hackathon and bring it to new heights. At UofTHacks, we bring people together to make new friends, learn new things, and bring new ideas to life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<img src="/assets/images/bg-about.svg" alt="" />

<section id="why" class="text text--inverse bg-uh-lightblue section--md">
  <header class="section-header">
    <div class="container container--sm text-center">
      <h1 class="section-header-title">Why Attend?</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="section-body">
    <div class="container container--sm">
      <p class="lead text-center">To try new things, meet new people, and to <br>take your skills to higher summits.</p>

      <p>
        Join us and <strong>499</strong> other brilliant developers, creative designers, and innovative creators for <strong>36 hours</strong> of hacking.
      </p>

      <p>
        With awesome hardware, APIs, and assistance provided to you by our sponsors, you will have the opportunity to build something you never thought was possible.
      </p>

      <p class="lead">
        All it takes is the willingness to try something new.
      </p>

      <p>
        You don't have to be a pro to attend. If this will be your <strong>first hackathon</strong>, we want you to expose you to the world of creation.
      </p>

      <p>

      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

